### API Endpoints
- [x] POST /api/discovery/scan — Start network scan
- [x] GET /api/discovery/scan — List all scans
- [x] GET /api/discovery/scan/{id} — Get scan details
- [x] GET /api/discovery/scan/{id}/status — Scan progress
- [x] GET /api/discovery/scan/{id}/results — Scan results (paginated)
- [x] POST /api/discovery/scan/{id}/cancel — Cancel scan
- [x] POST /api/discovery/scan/{id}/import — Import to hosts

