### Features Implemented
- Configurable scan rate (default: 100ms)
- Parallel goroutines (default: 50 concurrent, max 200)
- Port fingerprinting (SSH:22, RDP:3389, VNC:5900, HTTP:80, HTTPS:443, +6 more)
- OS detection via banner + port pattern + hostname analysis
- Results: IP, hostname, open ports, OS guess, response time
- Import results to hosts table (all or selected)
- Rate limiting to prevent abuse
- Skip loopback/link-local IPs
- CIDR validation (max /16)
- Pagination on results

